column5: I read from this site regarding the best internet marketing strategies that can be used to bring business to the next level. I thought it was interesting and decided to share.
someone go first and tell me if its all good?
Historically all the good marketing strategies originate in Ethiopia (where the posters IP goes back to).
I disagree,  I have recently profited from some lucrative ventures out of Nigeria.

Yes...there's a guy there who emailed me a once in a lifetime offer!!!  He has a gazillion dollars that he needs someone to put in the bank for him, and all I need to give him is my banking info and he'll deposit a cool billion for me!!  I gave him my life savings account...any day now, I'll be rich!!!  Cant wait!!  I was going to keep this a secret in case it didn't pan out, but I was too excited!
Hee Hee good one, I liked that
and Welcome to the board!!!  (couldn't resist)
